	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.73]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>D'oh! Forgot about lava storm and Unrest. Both are also great places to hunt. If your server is like mine, Unrest will have to be a bring your own group deal, as few people go there. Everyone seems to have trouble kiting in their teens. I eventually gave up kiting altogher, except for fear kiting in the pesky animals. (Snow cougers, griffs, etc.) I prefer to root'n'rot now. It's pretty mana effeciant once you have the Warden of Tunare Symbol. &lt;grins&gt;<br>&nbsp;<br>Tebyen Trueheart(druid)<br>Frizza (enchanter)<br>Tebyene (ranger)<br>Sikle (necromancer)<br>Senior Officer/Events Coordinater of Cold Comfort</td></tr>
